Package: ececplots
Type: Package
Title: ECEC/ECS Teams Visualization Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("ECEC/ECS Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "team@example.com")
Description: A dedicated visualization package for the ECEC/ECS teams.
    Provides standardized scatterplots and barplots with a consistent base
    frame that controls figure dimensions and panel layout. All plots share
    the same width/height dictionaries and load custom fonts from the
    package fonts directory. An Excel macro companion allows figures to be
    exported to Excel with the underlying data attached.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
